org.jboss.windup.graph.model

Interface ProjectDependencyModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame

    public interface ProjectDependencyModel
extends WindupVertexFrame
    Project dependency information. This has all of the information that would be required for a Maven dependency, but can also be used for non-maven dependencies. Additional interfaces may extend this to provide further functionality.
